    "title": "Job Opening Hotel Manager at Scootsy Holdings Services",
    "description": "Scootsy Holdings Services is actively seeking a talented and motivated Hotel Manager to join our dynamic team in Bhopal. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Scootsy Holdings Services:\nScootsy Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Learning & development budget\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Scootsy Holdings Services!",
